channel.title: Hello, I'm Oliver
channel.description:
Hi bootstrappers!
I've been listening to the podcast from the start and I'm caught up to when this forum was first setup. I thought I'd join in on the fun and claim my low digit user id.
I'm based in Seattle, working full time and dicking around with a side project I'm hoping to launch soon. Super excited to be apart of this engaged and constructive community!
Oliver
